data.title: Death Notice Judy DICKINSON
data.meta_description: We regret to inform you of the recent death of Judy DICKINSON
data.text:
The death has occurred of:

Judy DICKINSON (n√©e McNicholl)

8th July 2024 in Perth, W. Australia (formerly of Faughanvale), beloved wife of Bob, loving mother of Siobhan and Christopher, mother-in-law of Dave, devoted grandmother of Saoirse, daughter of the late Michael and Kathleen McNicholl and dear sister of Patrick, Helen, Hugh, Betty, Michael and Mary.

Requiem Mass will be celebrated in Star of the Sea Church, Faughanvale, on Wednesday 17th July 2024 at 7.30 pm. The Mass will be streamed live via the church webcam or the link below.

Our Lady of Lourdes pray for her.
